title: COVID19 SNOMED Value Set for Lymphoma
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains terms related to lymphomas and is listed as an immunocompromised condition on the CDC SARS-CoV-2 hospitalization surveillance case report form.),(Data Element Scope: ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes lymphomas.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes lymphoma in remission, personal and/or family history of lymphoma and complications of lymphoma.)
